These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: cola, hot-chocolate, fanta, mirinda
Pet: rat, chinchilla, ferret, frog
1. Pet:frog is on the left of Beverage:fanta##1
2. Beverage:cola is on the left of Pet:chinchilla##1
3. Beverage:mirinda is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:ferret is on the left or right of Pet:frog##3
5. Beverage:cola is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | cola | hot-chocolate | mirinda | fanta |
| Pet        | rat | chinchilla   | frog | ferret    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: drama, spy, time-travel, family
Nationality: argentine, brazilian, british, mexican
1. Movie-Genre:spy is on the left of Movie-Genre:family##1
2. Nationality:argentine is on the left of Nationality:british##1
3. Nationality:british is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:argentine == Movie-Genre:drama##1
5. Nationality:brazilian is on the right of Nationality:british##1
6. Nationality:argentine == Movie-Genre:drama##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | drama  | spy  | family |
| Nationality   | mexican    | argentine | british | brazilian    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: kale, peach, kiwi, lime
Movie-Genre: drama, adventure, fantasy, epic
1. Food:lime is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:epic##3
2. Food:kiwi is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:epic is on the left or right of Food:peach##3
4. Movie-Genre:epic is on the right of Movie-Genre:fantasy##1
5. Movie-Genre:drama is in an odd position##4
6. Food:peach is on the right of Food:kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | lime | kiwi | peach    | kale      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy        | epic     | drama | adventure |

