.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: rock-climbing, collecting, puzzles, skydiving
Music-Genre: ambient, trance, soul, funk
1. Hobby:collecting is between Music-Genre:ambient and Music-Genre:funk##2
2. Hobby:skydiving is on the left of Hobby:rock-climbing##1
3. Music-Genre:soul is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:trance is on the left of Music-Genre:funk##1
5. Music-Genre:trance is on the right of Hobby:rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | rock-climbing | collecting | puzzles |
| Music-Genre   | soul       | ambient   | trance    | funk  |

