.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: country, reggae, metal, soul
Nationality: italian, japanese, german, polish
1. Music-Genre:metal is on the right of Nationality:polish##1
2. Nationality:japanese == Music-Genre:soul##1
3. Nationality:german is on the right of Music-Genre:country##1
4. Music-Genre:reggae is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:metal is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:italian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | country    | metal   | soul       |
| Nationality   | italian | polish | german | japanese |

