.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: tea, iced-tea, sprite, water
Music-Genre: house, salsa, reggae, rock
1. Beverage:tea == Music-Genre:rock##1
2. Music-Genre:house is on the right of Beverage:tea##1
3. Music-Genre:rock is between Music-Genre:house and Beverage:sprite##2
4. Beverage:tea is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:rock is on the left or right of Music-Genre:house##3
6. Beverage:iced-tea is on the left or right of Music-Genre:salsa##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | sprite   | tea | water |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | salsa | rock        | house    |

